{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"case","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":[" If a text's language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out horizontally."]}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal","abstract":[],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"type":"topic","title":"MLNTextWritingMode","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection"}}}